## 1\. 整体架构：阳光通道流量路径

### 示意图

\!\[整体架构图\]\(NKRbbKyRgo8algxH4rdcEF3fnOd\)  \&lt;\!\-\- 图片链接可直接替换为实际图片地址 \-\-\&gt;

### 说明

- **中文**：本地设备（电脑 / 手机）通过 SSH 加密隧道连接海外 VPS，海外流量经由 VPS 转发访问 GitHub、YouTube 等海外服务；国内网站则直接直连，不经过隧道，保证国内访问的速度与稳定性。

- **英文**：Local devices \(laptop/smartphone\) connect to the overseas VPS via an encrypted SSH tunnel\. Overseas traffic is forwarded by the VPS to access services like GitHub, YouTube and Stack Overflow, while domestic websites are accessed directly without going through the tunnel to ensure speed\.

